29 12-8-701. Arkansas Amber Alert System.
30 (a) There is established the Arkansas Amber Alert System to be
31 administered by the Division of Arkansas State Police.
32 (b) The division shall:
33 (1) Serve as the coordinating law enforcement agency to alert
34 the public of abducted children through the Arkansas Amber Alert System; and
35 (2) Establish the criteria for activation of the Arkansas Amber
36 Alert System.
